  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (Tender, M&E)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Prepare plans, documents, and bill of quantities for supplier quotations and pricing analysis.</li>\n  <li>Source, compile, and evaluate supplier/vendor quotations based on tender requirements.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for detailed breakdown pricing, including material and labour cost estimation.</li>\n  <li>Handle tenders including scope of work, pricing schedules, and non-material requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Quantity Surveying</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of <strong>Project Tendering/Costing</strong> experience.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office Applications (Word, Excel &amp; PowerPoint).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
